extends layout

block content
  section(id="description")
    a(href="http://expressjs.com/", class="express") Express
    span(class="description") 
      a(href="https://nodejs.org/en/") Node.js
      |  için Hızlı, inatçı olmayan, minimalist bir web framework'üdür.

  div(id="install-command") $ npm install express --save

  section(id="intro")
    div(id="boxes", class="clearfix")
      div(id="web-applications")
        h3 Web Uygulamaları 
        | Express is a minimal and flexible Node.js web application framework that provides a robust set of features for web and mobile applications.

      div(id="apis")
        h3 API'ler
        | With a myriad of HTTP utility methods and middleware at your disposal, creating a robust API is quick and easy.
      
      div(id="performance")
        h3 Performans 
        | Express provides a thin layer of fundamental web application features, without obscuring Node.js features that you know and love.

      div(id="frameworks")
        h3 Frameworkler  
        | Many 
        a(href="http://expressjs.com/en/resources/frameworks.html") popular frameworks 
        | are based on Express.
